headline: ISRG's International Growth Outpaces US With 35% Procedure Volume
summary: Intuitive Surgical sees international procedures jump 23% in 2025, now 35% of total, outpacing U.S. growth and reshaping its long-term expansion strategy.

headline: Is It Worth Investing in Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) Based on Wall Street's Bullish Views?
summary: Based on the average brokerage recommendation (ABR), Intuitive Surgical (ISRG) should be added to one's portfolio. Wall Street analysts' overly optimistic recommendations cast doubt on the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric. So, is the stock worth buying?

headline: Intuitive Surgical’s AI And Da Vinci 5 Put Valuation In Focus
summary: Intuitive Surgical, ticker NasdaqGS:ISRG, has launched its Da Vinci 5 robotic system, adding new workflow and data capabilities to the operating room. The company is integrating artificial intelligence across its platforms to support robotic assisted procedures and improve decision support for clinicians.
